        <h2>
            人的本性与命运的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7207226">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7207226/" class="title-link">尼布尔《人的本性与命运》小摘要</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7207226"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47643947-54.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">江绪林</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-24"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-24 00:12:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7207226_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  【按语：Reinhold Niebuhr不是系统神学家，在《人的本性与命运》（1939）中他是以基督教先知身份来写作的。尼布尔酷似一个世纪之前的祁克果，不过祁克果是面对着形而上学的世界发言，而尼布尔则面对着政治世界发言，但两者本质上都是一样：将真正的希伯来信仰，尤其是圣经基督...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7207226_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7207226_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










