    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/28796/" target="_blank">存在之思</a>
                <span class="pl">(雾中悟)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1355263/" target="_blank">我的基督信仰Ⅱ</a>
